{"tid":446280,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"<一鋪翻身> 想入「港大電機電子」既同學仔 10 Nov 見！","createTime":"2017-10-24T07:11:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T19:06:43.000Z","uid":14170,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d16959a171876fe349e4be45310b9e004cf82963","tid":446280,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T07:11:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/24/121132_9615fb41a3f2c8c4ae52238f5d3d2a05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F24%2F121132_9615fb41a3f2c8c4ae52238f5d3d2a05.jpg&h=914be836&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&lt;&lt;香港大學電機電子工程系&gt;&gt; 非聯招DAS入學講座 &ndash; 直入HKU Year 3<br />\n轉載自: <a href=\"https://www.eee.hku.hk/events/das-admission-talk-for-high-diplomaassociate-degree-students/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eee.hku.hk%2Fevents%2Fdas-admission-talk-for-high-diplomaassociate-degree-students%2F&d=TeY7SAw3qJ28urUpDWKnMNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=c7995817\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eee.hku.hk/events/das-admission-talk-for-high-diplomaassociate-degree-students/</a><br />\n<br />\n日期: 2017年11月10日(星期五)<br />\n時間: 下午4時30分開始<br />\n地點: CPD-3.28, 香港大學百週年校園<br />\n<br />\n簡介<br />\n對香港大學電機電子工程系(HKUEEE)學士課程有興趣的申請人，如果你已經取得相關的高級文憑/副學士學位，或將於2018年8月前完成相關的高級文憑或副學士課程, 你可以申請非聯招DAS入學，繼續就讀工程系學士的高年級課程。<br />\n通過DAS入學的學生可以申請學分轉移, 並在2〜2.5年內畢業，令繼續升學或就業的道路更暢順。今次的講座， 我們會分享DAS的入學資訊和成功學生的故事，令你更了解HKUEEE! <br />\n<br />\n請點擊這裡了解更多詳情 <br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/WJfyab\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FWJfyab&d=TeY7SAw3qJ28urUpDWKnMNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=2b671bb2\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/WJfyab</a><br />\n<br />\n請點擊這裡報名 <br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/gKQedw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FgKQedw&d=TeY7SAw3qJ28urUpDWKnMNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=1115e571\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/gKQedw</a>"},{"pid":"fc