r />\nYear1 Common Engineering courses<br />\nYear2 EEE courses<br />\nYear3 EE courses<br />\nYear4 Electives ( 任揀 EEE 既科 take，ee ce CS EE 都揀得 )"},{"pid":"70a82045a6f801e2de24cae35b5cbfa1fdcbcf03","tid":446280,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:02:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>覺得HKU 都係變返EEE 好過分開EE 同ee</blockquote><br />\nYear1 Common Engineering courses<br />\nYear2 EEE courses<br />\nYear3 EE courses<br />\nYear4 Electives ( 任揀 EEE 既科 take，ee ce CS EE 都揀得 )</blockquote><br />\n只有 3 字頭既 course 被 major 限制，其他都係任揀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n為左滿足 HKIE ELL 既要求姐"},{"pid":"58cbb788ea9a6f12ba71f2f4c741a134f4889112","tid":446280,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:04:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>覺得HKU 都係變返EEE 好過分開EE 同ee</blockquote><br />\nYear1 Common Engineering courses<br />\nYear2 EEE courses<br />\nYear3 EE courses<br />\nYear4 Electives ( 任揀 EEE 既科 take，ee ce CS EE 都揀得 )</blockquote><br />\n只有 3 字頭既 course 被 major 限制，其他都係任揀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n為左滿足 HKIE ELL 既要求姐</blockquote><br />\n好似我咁<br />\nYear1 讀 engineering math &amp; phy + major intro<br />\nYear2 讀 電機電子既 intro <br />\nYear3 讀 電機 major 科<br />\nYear4 讀 CS intro 科 ( CS 2 字頭科 )<br />\n<br />\n畢業就係 BEng in Electrical Engineering"},{"pid":"735c8e93b71a9478703e7307cc9d25be7a44aa43","tid":446280,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:06:43.000Z","msg":"HKU 唔會為左就業而局限學生一定要點讀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算分左 major 都好彈性比你自己揀一部分既 Electives"},{"pid":"fc9679418d56b54f674c2f33297117d572b9242f","tid":446280,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:30:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a84e6f3434fcbb387d5a9258b6e2c965179758